    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> mustard seeds </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant and starting to pop</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced spring greens </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until tender with a slight bite – these are your <strong>mustardy greens</strong></p>",
