      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, transfer the<strong> cooked chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Return the <strong>pulled chicken</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>curry pie filling</strong></p>",
